.subckt bus_keeper A  WN_FB=1u WP_FB=2u
*.PININFO A:B
X2 Y A cmos_inv WN=15u WP=45u LLN=3u LLP=3u m=1
X1 A Y cmos_inv WN=WN_FB WP=WP_FB LLN=3u LLP=3u m=1
